data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous 5BR/4BA Two-Story home with Open Concept Kitchen overlooking the Breakfast Room and Family Room with Fireplace.  Granite countertops and stainless steel appliances as well as an eating area.  Separate dining room and formal living room. The Second floor features three Secondary Bedrooms with separate Walk-in-Closets, two Full Baths, and an enormous Owners' Suite with private Retreat, Dual Vanity Owner's Bath and large, personal Walk-in-Closets. Covered patio off the back with fenced yard, great for entertainment. Home is conveniently close proximity to South Park Shopping Center, Tanger Outlet, with very easy access to Interstate 75. This home is in excellent condition and ready for your family to create new memories for years to come.
